                       [ E P I S O D E ]

  The drama captures the events of May 1995, when Iraq was crippled 
  by sanctions after refusing to comply with inspections. Feeling 
  betrayed following the appointment of Saddams second son Uday as 
  the dictators successor, Hussein Kamel gave UN and CIA officials 
  information on the whereabouts of the countrys hidden weapons. 
  This act of disloyalty led to he and his brother being murdered 
  by their uncle.
